Upstream-Name: sfml-audio
Upstream-Contact: Sönke Hahn <shahn@joyridelabs.de>
Source: http://hackage.haskell.org/package/sfml-audio
Comment: This package ship contains a convenience copy of sfml-audio. Because
 it uses a not-yet released development version, we use it in Debian, until it
 is properly released an packaged.

